snippet.title: From Gin Amber Beauty to YOU - A Birthday Gift
snippet.description:
It's that time of year again. As my birthday comes and goes, I want to share in another year passed and offer each and every one of you a discount for my products. You all are incredible and I want to thank my subscribers and followers for being here, supporting me, and showing love and compassion through likes, comments, and your own personal stories and testimonials.

Thank you so much!

YOU HAVE 2 OPTIONS:
1st - 34% off for non-discounted products with code BDAY34
2nd - 20% off for already discounted products with code BDAY20
https://ginamber.com

**IMPORTANT:
Due to their already discounted nature, codes are not valid for subscription items.
